name: VNObservation
desc: The abstract superclass for analysis results.

items.name: var uuid: UUID
items.desc: A unique identifier assigned to the Vision observation.

items.name: var timeRange: CMTimeRange
items.desc: The time range of the reported observation.

items.name: var confidence: VNConfidence
items.desc: The level of confidence in the observation's accuracy, normalized to [0, 1.0].

items.name: typealias VNConfidence
items.desc: A type alias for the confidence value of an observation.
